    "/config/video_cookies/status": {
      "get": {
        "tags": [
          "admin"
        ],
        "summary": "Video Cookies Status",
        "description": "返回 cookies 当前状态，给前端 ``VideoCookiesGuide`` 组件渲染。\n\n返回字段（**全部稳定**，前端类型可对齐）：\n- ``source``: ``\"browser:<name>\"`` / ``\"file\"`` / ``\"none\"``\n              —— 即 ``settings.video_cookies_choice()`` 的结论\n- ``effective_path``: ``str | None`` —— 当前实际生效的文件路径（仅 source=file 时有）\n- ``managed_path``:   ``str``        —— 前端\"上传\"接口会写入的固定路径\n- ``managed_file``:   ``dict``       —— 上面这个文件的状态（exists/size/modified/domains）\n- ``whitelist_domains``: ``list[str]`` —— 当前白名单（前端展示\"我可以为这些站上传\"）\n- ``upload_max_bytes``: ``int``      —— 大小上限（前端预校验）",
        "operationId": "video_cookies_status_config_video_cookies_status_get",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "X-Admin-Key",
            "in": "header",
            "required": false,
            "schema": {
              "anyOf": [
                {
                  "type": "string"
                },
                {
                  "type": "null"
                }
              ],
              "title": "X-Admin-Key"
            }
          }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Successful Response",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "type": "object",
                  "additionalProperties": true,
                  "title": "Response Video Cookies Status Config Video Cookies Status Get"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "422": {
            "description": "Validation Error",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
